HEADWORD: Fractionate
<hw>Frac"tion*ate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To separate
(a mixture of chemical substances) into different portions or fractions,
as in the distillation of liquids.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

